description: If you’re in the mood for a mouthwatering menu on the roads of Rosedale then Matheney’z Mobile Food’z iz the right choice, fo sho. Tacos (with shrimp, catfish, chicken, and more), Cheesesteak Sandwiches, and BBQ Ribs so finger lickin' delicious... these are only a few of their specialty dishes. So start making your way over to Matheney’z (or make ‘em come to you) for amazing eats that will truly delight your inner foodie.
name: Matheny'z Mobile Food'z
